{"tid":327383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學校有蜂巢　竟築在蔣介石銅像下體","createTime":"2017-07-18T17:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T11:36:36.000Z","uid":45120,"like":321,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1671ceb0c51298950e42a7cb1e2a562ee74afa1","tid":327383,"uid":45120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170717/640_0fd6691d903f8c9915bd2a76de35c806.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170717%2F640_0fd6691d903f8c9915bd2a76de35c806.jpg&h=793d79b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃姓民眾向《蘋果》投訴表示，他前天發現台北市內湖高工的校園內，蔣介石銅像下體處有異樣；他看到該處有新築的蜂巢，認為蔣若有知，應該很痛苦。<br />\n《蘋果》無法聯繫上黃，不知他是否曾向校方反映。<br />\n內工總務主任張聖淵回應，學校有蜂巢很平常，現在放暑假，校園內人不多，應該不影響學生；他昨天已經發現蜂巢，這、一兩天就會處理掉。"},{"pid":"26bf2abe3a1a952ac5e709e5855dc77e61a2146b","tid":327383,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:11:11.000Z","msg":"前列腺增生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f663d2c213e32f9228075f7bdd70af69c8e77e1b","tid":327383,"uid":118298,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:11:23.000Z","msg":"巨峰提子"},{"pid":"5e595bb20fb50763ff288bf5ed6ceac58fb2eb68","tid":327383,"uid":80503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:12:12.000Z","msg":"ban<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed5dc8ca503b9cbaff77609bc29ff76056e35fa","tid":327383,"uid":82532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1654e492f652d5f0cf94a3a38facd6f4e18c6a","tid":327383,"uid":2111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:12:45.000Z","msg":"笑撚死"},{"pid":"608725a4d32477360082861c4c9ec460eefa854f","tid":327383,"uid":109886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"